            "title": "日股初段升8.81% 韩股升4.96%\r\n",
            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\"><br/>    日经平均指数初段报34,508.05点，升2,794.02点或8.81%。<br/><br/>南韩首尔综合指数初段报2,407.38点，升113.68点或4.96%。 (WL)</span>\n</div>",
